content: An inferior rip off of an app I used years ago. This app only works in portrait, looks cheesy, has a much less capable search, and has fewer knots. After some digging, I realized the older app is Knots 3D. Well worth the extra cost.
replyContent: Thank you for your feedback. Talking about rip-offs at a price of € 1.99 for 130 knots can only result in € 1.99 being too high a price for you.  Since your financial situation is so bad, I would reimburse you for the price.  The landscape mode for tablets is currently being worked on and wide nodes are also following.  greetings
